title: Ep. 718 - A Happy Garba Night - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Though Bhide, Sodhi fail getting tickets for Garba, the residents get into the show with the help of Jetha's contact. IN the meantime, Babita and Jetha are left behind. When Iyer comes to take them inside, he is left behind.

title: Ep. 719 - Iyer Gets A Call For An Interview - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer gets a call for an interview from a Tamil newspaper. Babita questions the need for an interview and Iyer explains the same. Iyer is excited to read his interview the next day.

title: Ep. 720 - Newspapers Are Exchanged - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: While Iyer is excited to read about his interview, the paper is exchanged in the morning. Iyer goes to everybody's house to search for the newspaper. Will he get the correct newspaper?

title: Ep. 721 - Iyer's Excitement - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer finally gets his newspaper and is happy to read the same. He wants to know who had played a prank on him and realizes it is Tapu. He apologizes to him too. Later, Iyer translates the interview to Babita.

title: Ep. 722 - A Deal For A New Fridge - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha gets ready to go out when he comes across Babita. He ignores Ahmed for the same reason. Later, Daya embarrasses Jetha in front of Babita. Babita insists on buying a new fridge to Iyer.

title: Ep. 723 - A Diwali Scheme - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Nattu Kaaka is upset over the fact that there are barely any customers that are coming to their shop. Even Jetha is amused over the fact that it is the Diwali time and there should be even more customers, to which Nattu Kaaka proposes a Diwali scheme

title: Ep. 724 - The Business Affairs - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer is lured in by a clever business man who's proposal struck him more favorable than Jetha's and wishes to change to him than going with Jetha's offer.

title: Ep. 725 - Jetha Gets Deceived By Iyer - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer gives a shock to Jetha when he tells him that he had already purchased a refrigerator that his friend had proposed since they got it for cheaper and thus putting Jetha in a huge loss.

title: Ep. 726 - Bhide's Handy Skills  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide, yet again proves to his family that he could repair the fairy lights that they've been using for ages. But seeing his not so handy skills, they accuse him of being a miser and ask him to get new decorations this time for Diwali.

title: Ep. 727 - Tapu's Emotional Blackmail - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu begins to emotionally blackmail Jetha by saying that since he has refused to pay him money, he'll end up selling all his toys that include the new bicycle that Jetha had purchased him recently, and goes on to blackmail him.

title: Ep. 728 - Celebrations At Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the residents are wishing each other happy new year as everyone has a pleasant time with each other as they celebrate the new year on a good start

title: Ep. 729 - Tapu Sena Beseech Bhide To Give A Ride - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: It's a typical day at Gokuldham where the kids are playing and having fun. Meanwhile, they meet Bhide and pester him to give them a short ride in the society, which ends up making them happy!

title: Ep. 730 - The Lottery Ticket Scam - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide seems to be lured by the lottery ticket and urges Taarak to give him a lottery ticket as well, as he believes he might have some luck in it since he's giving a hand at it!Bhide seems to be lured by the lottery ticket.

title: Ep. 731 - Bhide Gets A Bad Dream - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide wakes up from a bad dream where he realizes that the tickets he exchanged didn't end up benifitting him, and that Taarak might end up winning the lottery, if not exchanged at the earliest.

title: Ep. 732 - Bhide Wins The Lottery - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide family and Taarak family, both go to Jetha's house as they're the only ones who know how to read Gujarati. To Bhide's surprise, Daya reveals that Bhide has won the lottery! What will happen now? Watch to find out!
